{"tid":1921791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我搵到5個白宮聯署，就快到期，其中2個同YouTuber有關","createTime":"2020-03-12T07:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T13:52:32.000Z","uid":246588,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7036b1729b8568a0284a0de134b01e75bdb83a","tid":1921791,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"(1)3月12號即係今日到期！！！欠5萬幾個<br />\n香港人強烈希望美國能夠派遣聯邦調查局局長正式調查所有涉嫌犯罪（六月至十二月)<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-people-strongly-hope-usa-can-send-fbi-commissioner-formally-investigate-all-suspected-crime-jun-dec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-people-strongly-hope-usa-can-send-fbi-commissioner-formally-investigate-all-suspected-crime-jun-dec&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9laix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=38cfb766\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-people-strongly-hope-usa-can-send-fbi-commissioner-formally-investigate-all-suspected-crime-jun-dec</a><br />\n<br />\n(2)3月16號到期<br />\n向北京政府施加壓力要求對香港進行議會制改革<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-pressure-beijing-government-parliamentary-republic-reform-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fimpose-pressure-beijing-government-parliamentary-republic-reform-hong-kong&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9laix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=3a147811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-pressure-beijing-government-parliamentary-republic-reform-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n(3)3月17號到期<br />\n要求美國組成對中國違反了《化學武器公約》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/require-united-states-form-coalition-forces-against-china-china-violates-chemical-weapons-prohibition-conven\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequire-united-states-form-coalition-forces-against-china-china-violates-chemical-weapons-prohibition-conven&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9laix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=ec5d312d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/require-united-states-form-coalition-forces-against-china-china-violates-chemical-weapons-prohibition-conven</a><br />\n<br />\n(4)3月21號到期<br />\n請求youtube解釋為什麼對冠狀病毒主題審查youtuber或沒有廣告（黃色圖標）<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9laix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=89f42e16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a><br />\n<br />\n(5)3月18號到期<br />\nYouTube必須從香港民主人士YouTubers上載的視頻中刪除取消身份化狀態<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/youtube-must-remove-demonetization-status-videos-uploaded-hong-kong-pro-democracy-youtubers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fyoutube-must-remove-demonetization-status-videos-uploaded-hong-kong-pro-democracy-youtubers&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9laix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=8dbcfb76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/youtube-must-remove-demonetization-status-videos-uploaded-hong-kong-pro-democracy-youtubers</a><br />\n<br />\n學杜汶澤話齋：<br />\n『支持白宮聯署即係支持你自己！』<br />\n<br />\n簽完之後記得登入email搵確認email，先叫完成聯署<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"bc0d93bfce3070c77d6d73708a1fb62708e81fdc","tid":1921791,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"推一次，光復香港近一步"},{"pid":"9ea64132cdfd7b383ae6bad94789801cafc51898","tid":19217